T02TD1724E:91a-1: badzra b'a r'a h'i t'a ra sto tram /
T02TD1724E:91a-3: rdo rje phag mo sgrol ma la bstod pa /
T02TD1724E:91a-4: rje btsun ma sgrol ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1724E:91a-5: stong nyid snying rje phag mo che //
T02TD1724E:91a-6: sgrol ma'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1724E:91a-7: smra bsam brjod med pha rol phyin //
T02TD1724E:91a-8: sgrol ma'i gsung la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1724E:91a-9: dri med ye shes zla ba'i thugs //
T02TD1724E:91a-10: sgrol ma'i thugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1724E:91a-11: zla 'od srid pa'i mun sel ba //
T02TD1724E:91a-12: 'joms byed nyi ma'i dkyil dang mtshungs //
T02TD1724E:91a-13: thabs dang shes rab yon tan ldan //
T02TD1724E:91a-14: sgrol ma la ni rtag tu 'dud //
T02TD1724E:91a-15: 'gro la bu bzhin rtag tu gdung //
T02TD1724E:91a-16: srid gsum rnam thar gsum la 'god //
T02TD1724E:91a-17: seng ldeng nags la rab gnas shing //
T02TD1724E:91a-18: 'jigs pa brgyad las shin tu skyob //
T02TD1724E:91a-19: sgrol ma la ni phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1724E:91a-20: mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams su //
T02TD1724E:91a-21: rdo rje mkha' 'gror skur ston cing //
T02TD1724E:91a-22: 'gro ba'i sgrib gnyis sbyong mdzad pa //
T02TD1724E:91a-23: sgrol ma la ni phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1724E:91a-24: dpal dang ldan pa'i zhing khams su //
T02TD1724E:91a-25: rin chen mkha' 'gror skur ston cing //
T02TD1724E:91a-26: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal nad sel mdzad //
T02TD1724E:91a-27: sgrol ma la ni phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1724E:91a-28: bde ba can gyi zhing khams su //
T02TD1724E:91a-30: bde ba chen po'i dang la gnas //
T02TD1724E:91a-31: sgrol ma la ni phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1724E:91a-32: rnam par dag pa'i zhing khams su //
T02TD1724E:91a-33: las kyi mkha' 'gror skur ston cing //
T02TD1724E:91a-34: phrin las rnam bzhis 'gro don mdzad //
T02TD1724E:91a-35: sgrol ma la ni phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1724E:91a-36: mtha' dbus med pa'i zhing khams su //
T02TD1724E:91a-37: pha rol phyin ma'i skur ston cing //
T02TD1724E:91a-38: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas tshogs dang bcas //
T02TD1724E:91a-39: sgrol ma la ni phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1724E:91b-0: dur khrod @91b brgyad kyi zhing khams su //
T02TD1724E:91b-1: rdo rje phag mor skur ston cing //
T02TD1724E:91b-2: me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs //
T02TD1724E:91b-3: sgrol ma la ni phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1724E:91b-4: pandi ta zla ba grags pas bstod pa mdzad pa rdzogs so//
